quran[7{c,v,t}:
5,51,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho! yahudion aur esaion ko apna Rafeeq nah banaao, yeh aapas hi mein aik dosray ke Rafeeq hain aur agar tum mein se koi un ko apna Rafeeq banata hai to is ka shumaar bhi phir unhi mein hai, yaqeenan Allah zaalmon ko apni rahnumai se mahroom kar deta hai"
5,52,"tum dekhte ho ke jin ke dilon mein nifaq ki bemari hai woh aُnhi mein daud dhoop karte phirtay hain kehte hain"" hamein dar lagta hai ke kahin hum kisi museebat ke chakkar mein nah phas jayen"" magar baeed nahi ke Allah jab tumhe faisla kin fatah bakhshay ga ya apni taraf se koi aur baat zahir kere ga to yeh log apne iss nifaq par jisay yeh dilon mein chupaye hue hain nadim hon ge"
5,53,"aur uss waqt ahal imaan kahin ge"" kya yeh wohi log hain jo Allah ke naam se kari kari kasmain kha kar yaqeen dilatey thay ke hum tumahray sath hain ?"" un ke sab aamaal zaya hogaye aur aakhir-kaar yeh nakaam o namuraad ho kar rahay"
5,54,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho, agar tum mein se koi apne deen se phirta hai ( to phir jaye ) Allah aur bohat se log aisay peda kar day ga jo Allah ko mehboob hon ge aur Allah unn ko mehboob hoga, jo mominon par naram aur kufar par sakht hon ge, jo Allah ki raah mein jad-o-jehad karen ge aur kisi malamat karne walay ki malamat se nah dareen ge yeh Allah ka fazl hai, jisay chahta hai ataa karta hai Allah wasee zaraye ka maalik hai aur sab kuch jaanta hai"
5,55,"tumahray Rafeeq to haqeeqat mein sirf Allah aur Allah ka rasool aur woh ahal imaan hain jo namaz qaim karte hain, zkoh dete hain aur Allah ke agay jhuknay walay hain"
5,56,aur jo Allah aur is ke rasool aur ahal imaan ko apna Rafeeq bana le ussay maloom ho ke Allah ki jamaat hi ghalib rehne wali hai
5,57,"a y logo jo imaan laaye ho, tumahray paish ro ahal kitaab mein se jin logon ne tumahray deen ko mazaq aur tafreeh ka samaan bana liya hai, unhen aur dosray kafiroon ko apna dost aur Rafeeq nah banaao Allah se daro agar tum momin ho"
